    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Use to describe a type of mass-produced American furniture produced in Grand Rapids, Michigan, particularly between the 1850s and 1920s.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
